-- MOVES-Northland Capital names Patrick Claridge CEO
-- 
-- Wed Sep 10, 2014 06:16AM EDT
-- None



Sept 10 (Reuters) - London-based investment bank Northland Capital Partners Ltd said it appointed Patrick Claridge its chief executive with immediate effect.

Claridge has experience in advising both private and listed companies on capital raisings, with particular expertise in the growth company sector, Northland Capital said.